fields.name: XIAOMI
fields.description: Xiaomi is a popular Chinese technology company that manufactures a wide range of products, including smartphones. Known for its affordable yet feature-packed devices, Xiaomi has gained a strong following in the smartphone market.

fields.name: realme
fields.description: Realme is a relatively new smartphone brand that was established in 2018 as a subsidiary of the Chinese company, Oppo. Realme aims to provide affordable smartphones with powerful specifications and an emphasis on the latest trends and features.

fields.name: Apple
fields.description: Apple Inc. is a leading technology company known for its innovative products, and one of its most popular product lines is the iPhone, a series of smartphones. The iPhone has consistently been at the forefront of mobile technology and has a large and dedicated following worldwide.

fields.name: Samsung
fields.description: Samsung is another prominent technology company that manufactures a wide range of products, including smartphones. The Samsung Galaxy series, in particular, is highly popular and known for its advanced features and cutting-edge technology.

fields.name: HONOR
fields.description: Honor is a smartphone brand that was originally a subsidiary of Huawei, a well-known technology company. Honor smartphones are known for their high-quality build, innovative features, and competitive pricing. While maintaining a strong focus on delivering value for money, Honor devices offer a range of features and capabilities.

fields.name: Huawei
fields.description: Huawei is a global technology company that manufactures a wide range of products, including smartphones. Known for its innovative features, advanced technology, and high-quality devices, Huawei has gained recognition in the smartphone industry.
